VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \b(?:puts|print|logger\.(?:debug|info|error)|Rails\.logger\.(?:debug|info|error))\s*\(?.*(?:exception|backtrace)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:release|production
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects logging or printing of exception/backtrace details.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Stack Trace or Sensitive Exception Disclosure.
